  she was a member of the new york times reporting team that received the 2015 pulitzer prize for international reporting for coverage of the 2014 ebola virus epidemic in west africa.http://www.pulitzer.org/works/2015-international - reporting team members named by the times were pam belluck , cooper , sheri fink , adam nossiter , norimitsu onishi , kevin sack , and ben c. solomon.http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2015/04/20/business/media/21pulitzer - winners-finalists.html   at the wall street journal , cooper wrote about trade , politics , race , and foreign policy at the washington and atlanta bureaus from 1992 to 1997 .

